 2001-21832001-11-270,  ,  ,  ,  HERITAGE,  , 
PrecisAppointment of CHARLES DALFEN, of Nepean, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of CHARLES DALFEN as Chairman of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, effective January 1, 2002.
